        {
            "title": "AI打車時代來了！滴滴、阿里巴巴開啟「一句話叫車」新戰場 專家：出行生態將重構",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OJ7scWvPss_8jBfRxNOCiQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/acbe42583e71eea7281335d6186becde\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
